<H1 align=center>ADD/EDIT&nbsp; BANK/CREDIT CARD DETAILS – DC081</H1>
<P><FONT color=red>NOTE: areas shown in red are mandatory and must be completed 
to proceed</FONT></P>
<P><H3>Bank / Credit Card Owner: </H3>if the application is 
sole, the name will be populated with the applicant’s name and the field will be 
greyed out. If it is a joint application, select the card owner’s name from the 
drop-down list
<P></P>
<P><H3>Card Type: </H3>select this from the drop-down list eg. 
Visa, Access, Delta, Store, Cheque Guarantee
<P></P>
<P><H3>Card Provider: </H3>Enter the name of the card supplier 
(E.g. Barclaycard or Access)
<P></P>
<P><H3>Total outstanding balance / average monthly repayment: </H3>enter the amount outstanding and the average monthly repayment in the 
field. This will be considered in assessing affordability
<P></P>
<P><H3>Additional card holders: </H3>if the card is in joint 
names, click the ‘Yes’ radio button and enter the details in the field 
(‘additional card holder details’ field is mandatory, if there are any 
additional holders)
<P></P>
<P><H3>OK: </H3>clicking on ‘OK’ leads back to <A href="HELP_DC080.asp">Bank / Credit Card Details 
(DC080)</A>.

